widgets_values: The image is of a plain pink t-shirt with a round neckline. The shirt is made of a soft, lightweight fabric and has a slightly wrinkled texture. On the front of the shirt, there is a small embroidered design of three small hearts in a darker shade of pink. The hearts are arranged in a diagonal line, with the largest heart in the center and the smallest heart on the left side. The embroidery is done in a simple, minimalistic style. The background of the image is white, making the pink shirt stand out.
